And for the first prize,
they pull out ticket A.

25
00:01:12,020 --> 00:01:15,430
That's for the first prize.

26
00:01:15,430 --> 00:01:18,110
Now, when we think about who
could be pulled out for the

27
00:01:18,110 --> 00:01:24,000
second prize, it's only going
to be tickets B or C.

28
00:01:24,000 --> 00:01:25,800
Now the first prize could
have gone the other way.

29
00:01:25,800 --> 00:01:29,260
It could have been
A, B, and C.

30
00:01:29,260 --> 00:01:33,120
The first prize could have
