36
00:01:52,310 --> 00:01:54,440
So these are not independent
events.

37
00:01:54,440 --> 00:01:57,500
The second event-- the outcomes
for it, are dependent

38
00:01:57,500 --> 00:01:59,180
on what happened in
the first event.

39
00:01:59,180 --> 00:02:03,450
So they are not independent.

