44
00:02:14,170 --> 00:02:15,660
that ticket back in.

45
00:02:15,660 --> 00:02:16,780
Instead they taped
it to the prize.

46
00:02:16,780 --> 00:02:19,550
But if they put that ticket
back in, then the second

47
00:02:19,550 --> 00:02:22,260
prize, it would have still had
